title: Puscifer COMPLETE Discography (2003 - 2013)
description:
Puscifer is a side project of Maynard James Keenan, known for his work with the bands Tool and A Perfect Circle. As Keenan is the only permanent member and he considers the project to be his "creative subconscious", Puscifer could be considered a pseudonym for his solo work.
